  "elapsed_s": 12.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in Austro-Hungarian empire, well, everybody had to-- had to go into the empire, and you know, the empire had at least a half a dozen nationalities, or the nationals.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he's being a harness maker, he was sent into Hungary to the great Hungarian Plains, where there were the-- the, um, cattle herds and horse ranches.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he was sent to the stud farm there as a harness maker.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he served his three years there-- it was compulsory.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But in every year, every spring, for about four-- four months from that central stud farm there, they sent out in the surrounding-- the surrounding area in the-- in the province, the stud farms where two or three or four depended on the-- on the agricultural area.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he was sent out to the village, then finally where he met up with my-- with my mother.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Or to round out the story, uh, the farmers around here who were, uh, led their mares into the stud farms-- where my father was the commander in the-- in the rank of sergeant major-- and the farmers found out, and saw his work as a-- as a harness maker.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They begged him to be [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He was going to be discharged from the army, going back to the village, and they're going to do everything they can to-- rent him a house, or give him a house, and so just open up a shop because they had no-- no harness make in the-- in the district there.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And so he did, he came back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he had so much work, so much work that he needed an apprentice.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
